msgid "IndexNow is enabled but I'm not seeing pings."
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/help-tabs.php:240
msgid "Check three things: (1) the IndexNow API Key field is filled, (2) you're publishing a public post type — revisions and autosaves are skipped, (3) you're on production. Pings are non-blocking, so failures are silent — check your server log for requests to api.indexnow.org."
